    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. Honestly, it's in such incredible shape that it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been pampered and kept in truly pristine condition\u2014you won't find a single thing out of place. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Drop me a message, I'd love to tell you more about it!",
