      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 in collector-quality condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp with a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically flawless, the Double VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe has been preemptively reinforced to ensure long-term structural integrity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers tactile, precise gates, paired with a fresh clutch and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The suspension maintains perfect geometry with zero bushing deflection, preserving the communicative chassis balance this platform is known for. Every fluid service is documented, and the exterior retains its factory luster with consistent paint depth across all panels. This is a visceral, naturally aspirated masterpiece for the discerning enthusiast.",
